As a case manager for the firm, I'm currently handling a complex lawsuit identified as "CASE-12345". We have four parties involved: two plaintiffs named "Emma Johnson" and "Liam Smith", and two defendants named "Sophia Williams" and "Oliver Brown". I require assistance with organizing their roles accurately. Furthermore, we have accumulated a vast array of case documents that need to be catalogued. They include "Legal Briefs", "Witness Statements", "Court Orders", and "Evidence Submissions". Lastly, the case has critical milestones which must be meticulously tracked, including "Initial Hearing" set for May 15, 2023, "Discovery Completion" due by July 20, 2023, and "Trial Start" scheduled for November 5, 2023. 

Could you please perform the following tasks:
1. Categorize the involved parties by their roles in Case "CASE-12345".
2. Index all the relevant documents by their titles and types for this case.
3. Set up a detailed timeline for the case proceedings, inclusive of the aforementioned milestones.

Here are the specific details for each task:

For categorizing parties:
- Case ID: "CASE-12345"
- Parties: 
  - { name: "Emma Johnson", role: "Plaintiff" }
  - { name: "Liam Smith", role: "Plaintiff" }
  - { name: "Sophia Williams", role: "Defendant" }
  - { name: "Oliver Brown", role: "Defendant" }

For indexing documents:
- Case ID: "CASE-12345"
- Documents: 
  - { title: "Complaint", type: "Legal Brief" }
  - { title: "Defendant Memo", type: "Legal Brief" }
  - { title: "Affidavit of Emma Johnson", type: "Witness Statement" }
  - { title: "Affidavit of Liam Smith", type: "Witness Statement" }
  - { title: "Court Injunction", type: "Court Order" }
  - { title: "Photo Evidence", type: "Evidence Submission" }

For setting up the case timeline:
- Case ID: "CASE-12345"
- Milestones:
  - { name: "Initial Hearing", due_date: "2023-05-15" }
  - { name: "Discovery Completion", due_date: "2023-07-20" }
  - { name: "Trial Start", due_date: "2023-11-05" }

Please execute these function calls to assist in optimizing our case management processes.

I would like to enhance our telecom CRM system with several updates. Firstly, I need to update the profile of a customer, John Doe, with ID "JD_8098". His new address is "1234 Telecom Lane, Datacity, DC 90909", his email has changed to "john.doe@email.com", and his phone plan should now be set to "Unlimited Data Plan". Secondly, I want to track service usage patterns for customer Jane Smith, ID "JS_1002", from "2023-03-01" to "2023-03-31". Lastly, we need to manage a support ticket with ID "TKT_4321" by updating its status to "Resolved" and adding resolution notes saying "Replaced faulty router, service restored". Additionally, we aim to analyze customer feedback to improve our service. Attached is the JSON file containing feedback data from our customers within the last quarter.

Please call the necessary functions with these specifics to assist with the task:

1. Update John Doe's customer profile with the new information mentioned.
2. Track Jane Smith's service usage for the specified period.
3. Update the support ticket status for TKT_4321 with appropriate resolution notes.
4. Analyze the provided customer feedback data for service improvement insights.

